/>\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>King's Raid韓文公告：</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://cafe.naver.com/kingsraid/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcafe.naver.com%2Fkingsraid%2F&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cc9c4291\" target=\"_blank\">http://cafe.naver.com/kingsraid/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【公會】申請表/請假表</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>《King's Raid - 王之逆襲》<br />\n繁體中文版維基網址</strong></span></span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/y9RVvg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fy9RVvg&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cc300457\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/y9RVvg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King Raid's 歐洲人逐個捉</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid Friend List</strong></span></span><br />\n歡迎各巴絲留低ID 加好友啦喂<br />\n(記得每日送心先有本錢溝囡)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nQ：英雄自選劵揀咩英好?<br />\nA：有愛&gt;一切<br />\n依隻驚無勁唔勁，只有夾唔夾<br />\n同埋官方會因應英雄強弱而作出Buff同Nerf嘅調整<br />\n今個版本可能弱勢啲，但下個版本可能變神角都未定<br />\n所以不如揀咗有邊隻英係你真係鍾意嘅，想用嘅<br />\n再係Post度問下有咩組合可以夾佢，咁會比較好<br />\n相信各巴絲都好樂意為新手巴絲們解答的<br />\n<br />\nQ：需唔需要刷首抽架？<br />\nA：無首抽依回事，因為唔係抽返嚟，係可以直接用英雄自選卷換返嚟(新英除外)<br />\n【新手一定會有一張二星同三星英雄自選劵】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6326f8e97fee221f2850071ab43bbb8232a52ff0","tid":676693,"uid":22942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"大佬係132呀"},{"pid":"52c9b30c13ad0edb9caf1e669257bdfdf0a1b228","tid":676693,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6326f8e97fee221f2850071ab43bbb8232a52ff0","tid":676693,"uid":22942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"大佬係132呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"再開 sor"},{"pid":"1f512007f75da134c45df06ebe661272d16c12e8","tid":676693,"uid":67,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebe4d86be0971b737b208ec68212b4d39e22042","tid":676693,"uid":28631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"想問cuw 係咪分解佢算？仲有冇其他用途？"}]}